Description:
ClimaSys forced vent. IP54, 560m3/h, 230V, with outlet grille and filter G2.Label:Prisma-range:ClimaSys-product certifications:{}-product name:ClimaSys CV-product or component type:fan-range compatibility:{"1":"2018-04-13 02:29:17","2":"2018-04-13 02:29:17"}-type of ventilation filter:standard-air flow:{"1":"2018-04-13 02:29:17","2":"2018-04-13 02:29:17"}-[Us] rated supply voltage:{"1":"2018-04-13 02:29:18"}-input voltage:{"1":"2018-04-13 02:29:17"}-Range Presentation:
- Prisma: kit solutions for tested and IEC 61439-1&2 compliant low voltage electrical distribution switchboards - Prisma G: wall-mounted and floor-standing enclosures for electrical switchboards up to 630A, Icw 25kA rms/1s - Prisma P: cubicles for electrical switchboards up to 4000A, Icw 100kA rms/1s - Technical data:
- Metal enclosures: steel metal sheet with electrophoresis treatment + hot-polymerised polyester epoxy powder
- Color white RAL 9001
- Degree of protection IP30 to IP55
- Degree of protection against mechanical impacts IK07 and IK10Refer to the offer Prisma PH for specific applications in harsh environment : reinforced IP degree of protection, seismic withstand…-Range Benefits:Pooling our energies for building safety
- Prisma contributes to optimum safety of persons as well as to high reliability and continuity of service of the electrical installation.
- All components (switchgears, busbars, distribution blocks, prefabricated connections, etc.) are rated and coordinated for joint operation.
- All the most demanding switchboard configurations have been tested and are IEC standard compliant. - Prisma allows production of optimised, safe and simple switchboards to exactly meet your needs. - Prisma can be upgraded easily at any time without its original performance being affected, thanks to prefabricated and modular design. - Prisma is designed and manufactured in France, and available world-wide.-Range Application Presentation:Low voltage distribution and control switchboards for commercial and industrial buildings
- Data and Telecom (data centres, server rooms, telecom networks) - Retail (multi users centres, chain and independent retails) - Hospitality (hotels, collective residences) - Industrial buildings (non critical process, logistic, agricultural) - Health (hospitals, clinics, nursery houses) - Offices - Education - Sports - Leisure and culture

Title: Schneider set of 4 polyamid wall mounting lugs for PLM3025 to 108 NSYPFPLMG
Description:
set of 4 polyamid wall mounting lugs for PLM3025 to 108.Label:Thalassa PLM-range:Thalassa-accessory / separate part category:fixing accessory-product or component type:wall fixing support-device application:multi-purpose-mounting location:top and bottom, on rear of the enclosure-Range Presentation:Wall mounting polyester enclosures & accessories
Body and door made from fibreglass reinforced polyester, moulded by hot compression, RAL7035 colour. Same finish for all surfaces.
Features:
- 8 dimensions from 310x215x160mm up to 1056x852x350mm.- Bosses for fixation points are moulded, inserts included.- 2 locks with double-bar insert or 1 lock system with 3 action points.- Version with plain or glazed door.- Version with metallic or Bakelite mounting plate.- ATEX black colour version, plain door.- Total insulation suitable to produce class II assemblies.- Degree of protection IP66.- Impact resistance: IK10 for plain door version, - IK08 for the glazed door.- Self-extinguish: HB40- 960 ºC test withstanding.Certifications:
- Bureau Veritas - IEC62208 enclosure standard.- UL508A – CAN/CSA-C22.2Polyester plinths ZM 200 mm, stackable 2x200mm, for PLM75, PLM 86, PLM108 enclosures-Range Benefits:Polyester monobloc universal wall-mounting enclosure 
- No electrical contact risks. - Suitable for indoor or outdoor use. - Resistant to harsh atmospheres. - Can be used in a large temperature range. - Easy to machine and the machining does not produce corrosion. - Halogen free. - Light weight gives an easy installation. - Long life lasting without maintenance. - Strong : monobloc and IK10. - Assuring a good protection of equipment (IP66). - Integrated canopy, assuring always the same quality. - Reversibility for installation right or left door opening. - Locking system is out the protected volume. - Large door opening (180º). - Suitable for quick installation of DIN rails. - Easy door machining help thanks to the grid pattern on the back of the door. - A broad number of composition accessories. - A broad number of mounting systems, common with steel and stainless steel wall-mounting ranges. - Chassis and accessories for modular distribution. - Customise service: colour, machining, mounting accessories, locks. - Plinths available for big dimensions enclosures – ZM range 200 mm height-Range Application Presentation:
- Electrical distribution and Control- Infrastructures and Industry- Indoor, outdoor and harsh environments- Public areas thanks to total insulation – safety- Automation, measurement, distribution and protection - ATEX version for potentially explosive atmosphere

- other dimensions,

- One-piece folded and welded body, double plate thickness gutter shaped front profile. Flat rear panel. - Degree of protection: IP 66 for all single door enclosures, IP 55 for double door enclosures. - A light and resistant enclosure with folded cross structure sheet steel. - External mechanical impact resistance: IK 10 for enclosures with plain door, IK 08 for enclosures with glazed door. - Time saving : 54 dimensions with or without plain chassis, customized offer, wide range of accessories... - Wide range of sizes : from 300X200X150 to 1400X1000X300.  - Choice : plain door or glazed door. - Paint finish : colour grey RAL 7035. - Certifications : EN 62208 (LCIE), UL, CUL, BV, DNV, LR, GL, ATEX (modified enclosure).A complete range of applicative enclosure :
- Spacial S3DEX WM ATEX (10 dimensions) - Spacial S3DM Modular distribution enclosureA complete range of enclosures that can be equipped with modular chassis comprising 10 references from 24 to 240 modules :
- Spacial S3DB Terminals enclosure. - An offer developed for centralization and transmission of signals in industrial installations or on machines.And also...
- Spacial S3CM Control and dialogue system. - CaSys VDM 19" network and electronics enclosure.-Range Benefits:Your ideal universal enclosure designed for time saving !
- Global approach universal enclosure with dedicated accessories regarding the application. - Optimized approach regarding the application with Spacial S3D dedicated enclosure (dimensions) with dedicated accessories. - Customization services (configurated offer and specific solutions). - Water tightness : 
IP66 for single door and IP55 for double door. - Ruggedness : 
IK 10 for plain door and IK08 for glazed door. - Durable : with high UV resistance, treated hinges, aluminium hinge pins. - Smart : Door easily removable and reversible with double thickness 20 mm return fold for excellent rigidity, 120° opening, 2 or 3 concealed hinges. 3 closure points from height 600 mm with single operating point. Simple reversal of linkage. Maximum loading: 50 kg/m2. - Choice (enclosures) :
- with or without plain chassis
- with plain or glazed door, double door range
- dedicated dimensions to applications. - Choice (accessories) :
- plain chassis, silk-screened chassis, micro perforated chassis, telequick perforated chassis, symmetrical chassis,
- steel cable gland plate with grid pattern, steel cable gland plate with knock-outs aluminium cable gland plate cable gland plate with membranes. - Smart : hinges easily released and captive for easier door removal and door reversal. Wide choice of inserts. - Attractive : chamfered door edge, plasma welded, paint epoxy-polyester colour RAL 7035. - Adaptable : These enclosures can be supplied on request with :
- alternative colours,
- accessories pre-mounted,
- special machining,
- other dimensions,
- alternative finishes (zinc chromate, metallization, etc.) - Safety for people : 2 welded earth studs (on door and body). - Time saving : 
- 4 welded back studs shouldered 10mm for direct mounting of chassis,
- Wall mounting brackets fixed from the outside
- Wide choice of cable gland plate that can be equipped with quick cable entrance.
- Wide choice of chassis (silk-screened chassis, micro-perforated chassis, perforated chassis ....). - Services : Colours, dimensions, mounting of accessories through or customized service (configurated and specific offer).-Range Application Presentation:Industrial automation and industrial control
- Dedicated enclosure with EMC enclosure S3HF (10 dimensions). - Dedicated enclosure with terminal enclosure S3DB (11 dimensions). - And a wide choice of accessories chassis, cable entrance and cable management.Electrical distribution
- Dedicated enclosure with Spacial S3DM (8 dimensions enclosure with Depth 150mm).Electronics and Industrial Networks
- Dedicated enclosure Spacial VDM (equipped with 19'' frame).

· Linergy TRR Spring terminal blocks: fast and easy solution with high vibration resistance and extensive accessories range

Linergy TR terminal blocks are designed to ensure easy and fast installations, while providing the reliable performance you expect from a top-quality terminal block.

Title: Schneider SPRING TERMINAL, FEED THROUGH, 3 POINTS, 2,5MM², GREY NSYTRR23
Description: Linergy TR is terminal block for Linergy. It belongs to linergy passthrough terminal block with 2.5 mm² nominal cross section. The rated operational voltage is 600V conforming to CSA/cURus and 800V conforming to EN/IEC 60947-7-1. The rated current is 24A conforming to EN/IEC 60947-7-1 and 20A conforming to CSA and cURus. It is compliant with Green Premium (RoHS/REACH).

Title: Schneider Harmony, Modular timing relay, 0.7 A, 1 s..100 h, multifunction, solid state output, 24...240 V AC RE17LMBM

Title: Schneider Harmony, Interface plug-in relay pre-assembled, 5 A, 2 CO, with LED, with lockable test button, with protection circuit, 24 V DC RXG22BDPV
Description: This interface Plug-In relay belongs to the Schneider Electric Harmony electromechanical relays range. This is a pre-assembled standard cover relay mounted on a separate contact terminal socket with integrated clamp and a diode protection module. This is a 5A, 24Vdc, 2 CO interface mechanical relay. This pre-mounted relay is a ready-to-go package saving assembly time. The standard cover relay offers single-step lockable test button and LED indicator. The interface relay socket connection is by screw connector type. This pre-assembled relay weighs 0.067Kg.  Its design fit for industrial machines, packaging, textile, HVAC, automation control panels, low/medium voltage switchgear, motor controls, PLC Interfaces, power supplies, building or medical equipment, lighting controls. It is a green premium product and conforms to international standard and certifications like IEC, UL, EAC, CSA, ROHS and REACH.  It is sold in lots of 30.  The RXG plug-in relays are a series of industrial plug-in relays designed for both simple and complex automation systems and available with 1 CO (10A) and 2 CO (5A) contacts.

Title: Schneider Harmony, Miniature plug-in relay, 12 A, 2 CO, with LED, with lockable test button, 24 V DC RXM2AB2BD
Description: RXM miniature relays are part of Harmony Electromechanical Relays. This is a plug in relay to be mounted on a RXZE socket. It is a 2 C/O relay with current rating of 12A, control circuit voltage of 24 V DC. It also offers one-step loackable test button and mechanical indicator for contact status. The testbutton is activated momentarily by pushing the blue pushbutton on the front and locked by flipping up the green part. The mechanical indicator is next to the testbutton, where an orange flag indicates the relay contact status. A green LED on the front will illuminate when the relay is on. Status display with LED: clearly signal both in the day and night.  Its design is fit for industrial machines, packaging, textile, HVAC, automation control panels, low/medium voltage switchgear, motor controls, PLC Interfaces, power supplies, building or medical equipment, lighting controls. It is a green premium product and conforms to international standard and certifications like IEC, CE, UL, CSA, EAC, Lloyd's, RoHS and REACH. RXM Relay should be used with a RXZE socket (screw clamp, screw connector, push-in terminal). To protect against vibrations, plastic/metal clamp can be added to the socket. Protection modules and marking legend are also available. It is sold in lots of 10 and reference includes relay only.  The RXM plug-in relays are a series of industrial plug-in relays designed for both simple and complex automation systems and available with 2 CO (12A), 3 CO (10A), 4 CO (6A) contacts, 4 CO (3A) low level contacts.

Title: Schneider TeSys Vario - emergency stop switch disconnector - 25 A - back of enclosure VCCF0
